data.value: Since everyone organises their photos in their own way, we use convention syntax to account for that. Your copied files will all be named/placed however you specify above. It uses certain letter codes like "YYYY" or "CM" or "THH" to represent data specific to each image, and the rest of the text is the same for every image. You can see some common codes below, and a full list with the link at the bottom.
